title: Ladycat volleyball team nabs first win
text:
Ladycat volleyball team nabs first win By Debbie Holmes Posted: 10/01/2015 11:54:05 AM MDT Click photo to enlarge Estes Park junior Kaylee Coleson spikes the ball during an earlier match against Wiggins. The Ladycats earned their first win on Monday. « » 
The Ladycat volleyball team captured its first win the season. 
The ladies traveled to Strasburg on Monday, Sept. 26 and earned their first league win from Strasburg in a four-game match. 
The four-game series went; (Estes-Strasburg) 25-16, 23-25, 25-21, and then Estes struck it home in the fourth 25-22. 
This gives the Ladycats 1-6 league record overall in their tough Patriot League. The team stands at 1-12 in overall play for the season. 
Estes host Strasburg at home on Thursday, Oct. 1 and then is off until Oct. 20 when it will host Valley. Advertisement
